        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-05-20 18:47:21.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nDo you know if the ONAP CI machines support nested Virtualization? That needs to be enabled before you can run this.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "e5846b2e791bb109cbd1e298d0ddda0b016742d4",
